            "text_1": "<p>\"This is one of my go-to recommendations for patients concerned with forehead lines and skin creasing. The medical-grade silicone helps lock in moisture, smooth fine lines, and support the skin’s natural repair process overnight. It’s reusable, non-invasive, and great for anyone looking for a quick, visible skin refresh—no needles required.\"</p>",
