        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Benefits",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Wrinkle Smoothing –</strong> Visibly reduces the appearance of forehead lines and frown wrinkles by gently compressing the skin overnight.<br/><br/><strong>Firming Effect –</strong> Supports skin elasticity and boosts natural collagen repair for a firmer, more youthful-looking forehead.<br/><br/><strong>Hydration Boost –</strong> Locks in moisture to plump and smooth the skin’s surface while preventing overnight dehydration.<br/><br/>Clinically Tested and Dermatologist Approved.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QnkEdx": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does it work?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>You may use the wrinkle forehead patch overnight. <br/><br/>It is designed to be worn while you sleep and draws moisture into the skin and helps smooth out fine lines. The patch gently compresses the skin to prevent movement, reduce creasing, and improve skin texture. <br/><br/>With consistent use, it can help support collagen production and visibly reduce the appearance of forehead wrinkles.<br/><br/>To maximize its effectiveness, apply it to clean, dry skin before bed and remove it in the morning—then rinse, store, and reuse as needed.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! All skin types, including sensitive skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_kwzWVt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ingredients",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><p><strong>Salicylic Acid (BHA) - </strong>It penetrates pores to exfoliate and control excess sebum.<br/><br/><strong>AHA Lactic Acid - </strong>It helps remove dead skin cells from the surface of the skin, promoting a smoother and brighter complexion.<br/><br/><strong>Glycerin - </strong>Humectants that draw moisture into the skin, ensuring it stays hydrated.<br/><br/><strong>Sodium Hyaluronate - </strong>A smaller form of hyaluronic acid that deeply hydrates and plumps skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Delivery",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Return & Exchange Policy",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        }
      },
